{
  "stem": "17606.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 15.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "Finally, I open the door and I see Ukrainian SSes sitting there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "And there's a door leading to the next street.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "From [NON-ENGLISH] they are back to back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "I said, that will be-- that's my escape route.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "I closed a bit the door, put the swastika on, and went in and started to curse them in German.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "They didn't understand.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "One word, my German also was a lot to desire.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "I started cursing [NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And they say, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "I said, I'll be back in 10 minutes.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "I want to have that room sparkling clean.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "And I said, heil Hitler, and went out through the other door.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "That's how I vanished.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "I was a free man again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "Because everything-- what we were doing in those days is without thinking.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "Their actions worked faster than the brains.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "Because we would think we would never do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "So every action, every move, was faster than the brains.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "Although they say the brains work much faster.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "It's not true.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "Not in our case, anyhow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "Then again, I think that's why I got the medal on the Polish-- I got the medal for bravery and two bars.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "That was the highest medal for bravery, the two bars.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "And my name remained Jan Bednarczyk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "That's how I worked them still the end of the war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "Then come the Polish uprising.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was-- my group was in the old city Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's where the first battle was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were also the first group to be evacuated from over there, to central Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had to go through a tunnel, cut in the middle of the streets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the German was on the sides.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We cut through a tunnel in the middle.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They took us by.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
